This paper proposes a novel approach for unsupervised active learning for regression, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed approach is evaluated on various datasets from different domains, including computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The approach also involves optimization techniques, which can be related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.CV, cs.DS, and cs.CL.
